Title: Stupid Tools | Obiter dicta
Description:
I looooove building tools.
It’s like building a jig1 in a woodshop.
Once you’ve built your new tool, you feel like you now have the ability to do
something you couldn’t do before, or at least the ability to do it better.
Unlike a jig in a woodshop, with computer work we can store as many of these
tools as we want, as long as we can organize the github gists and
git project scripts directories.
